  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A red notice from the weather",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Meteorological Department warns that due to the activation of southwest monsoon, the wind speed may increase to 60-70 kilometers per hour from time to time in offshore areas from Puttalam to Colombo, Galle and Hambantota and Pottuvil.",
        "The sea areas can be very rough and there is a possibility that the sea waves can rise up to 2.5 - 3.5 meters in those areas.",
        "There is also a possibility of sea waves reaching the land from Puttalam to Colombo, Galle to Matara.",
        "Therefore, the Department of Meteorology advises not to engage in fishing and navigational activities in the sea areas off the coast from Colombo to Hambantota via Galle for the next 24 hours."
      ],
